There are always a bunch of ubers bitching when something they did earlier is made easier for others. To me, removing the key requirement, or making the key easier to obtain, would make perfect sense. Its not &quot;challenging&quot; to sit 10 hours in the Karnor basement camping a boring skeleton. Its just time consuming and boring. <br>
<br>
The prime reason for going to VP is getting Kunark spells, and now they upped spell drop rates, which hardly will make VP more popular among the high end guilds. <br>
<br>
